[gd_scene load_steps=7 format=3 uid="uid://calimaeventart1"]

; Event artifact — event / route-tied pieces (this is what carriers present as). Open this
; scene to change the model and to add/move/remove ArtifactConditionDecal children (each is
; a condition; the texture file name decides type + cleaning tool). "Randomized Decal
; Count" on the root picks how many of the placed conditions appear per run (re-rolled each
; loop / new save). 0 = always show them all.

